with an illegal firearm.

508
00:44:41,617 --> 00:44:43,953
[sighs] What was he planning to do here?

509
00:44:45,788 --> 00:44:49,250
Also, who's the guy he was with?

510
00:44:53,087 --> 00:44:54,547
Trace the gun's origin.

511
00:44:55,131 --> 00:44:56,924
Run a DNA analysis on this blood sample.

512
00:44:57,008 --> 00:44:58,259
I'm on it.

513
00:44:58,342 --> 00:45:01,345
[phone buzzing]

514
00:45:04,265 --> 00:45:05,266
Yes, talk.

515
00:45:05,975 --> 00:45:07,143
What?

516
00:45:07,727 --> 00:45:08,853
