524
00:45:38,716 --> 00:45:41,260
His name is Lee Suhyeong.
He used to be a detective.

525
00:45:42,345 --> 00:45:43,346
Lee Suhyeong?

526
00:45:44,472 --> 00:45:45,681
Why does it ring a bell?

527
00:45:45,765 --> 00:45:48,851
His wife was kidnapped
and murdered a few years back.

528
00:45:48,934 --> 00:45:51,395
He went rogue,
was suspended, and then retired.

529
00:45:52,229 --> 00:45:54,482
-Right, from Dongin PD?
-Yes, sir.

530
00:45:57,610 --> 00:45:58,652
Who called it in?

531
