We couldn't get an ID.
The call was from a burner phone.

532
00:46:01,822 --> 00:46:03,199
And it was a bit unusual.

533
00:46:03,699 --> 00:46:06,660
The caller said the victim
had chest trauma and internal bleeding

534
00:46:06,744 --> 00:46:07,870
due to the crash,

535
00:46:07,953 --> 00:46:09,997
and then claimed
that the crash was deliberate.

536
00:46:10,081 --> 00:46:12,625
He requested that an ambulance
and police be dispatched.

537
00:46:14,335 --> 00:46:16,712
Captain, could it have been Kang Taeju?

538
00:46:17,421 --> 00:46:19,256
Could he also have crashed
into Lee Suhyeong?

539
00:46:19,340 --> 00:46:22,468
We can't be sure yet, but he's certainly
got something to do with it.

540
00:46:22,551 --> 00:46:25,471
Detective Oh, we got the address.

541
00:46:26,138 --> 00:46:27,973
We've got the address for Lee's residence.

542
00:46:28,057 --> 00:46:29,392
Where is it?

543
00:46:31,018 --> 00:46:33,020
[♪ pensive music playing]

544
00:46:33,104 --> 00:46:36,107
[panting]

545
00:46:44,782 --> 00:46:46,492
[Mr. Noh] This is the end of our deal.

546
00:46:48,119 --> 00:46:51,038
You can consider your wife dead now.

547
00:46:51,622 --> 00:46:52,790
My wife

548
00:46:54,041 --> 00:46:57,128
was already dead by the time
I was supposed to meet the culprit.

549
00:46:58,295 --> 00:47:01,132
He was never going to let her live.

550
00:47:02,758 --> 00:47:04,969
You think it's different this time?

551
00:47:12,143 --> 00:47:14,645
[panting]

552
00:47:28,534 --> 00:47:30,369
[straining]

553
00:47:32,913 --> 00:47:37,501
[grunts, panting]

554
00:47:38,169 --> 00:47:39,170
[sighs]

555
00:47:43,674 --> 00:47:45,426
[♪ tense music playing]

556
00:48:00,191 --> 00:48:01,525
NAME: PARK GYEONGMIN

557
00:48:14,747 --> 00:48:16,832
VICTIM'S SHIRT BUTTON
INTENTIONALLY REMOVED

558
00:48:16,916 --> 00:48:18,542
EVIDENCE NO. 2
DATE: FEBRUARY 1, 2020

559
00:48:25,382 --> 00:48:26,800
Okay, thank you.

560
00:48:32,765 --> 00:48:34,892
-[music ends]
-[vehicle approaching]

561
00:48:34,975 --> 00:48:37,770
NAMGANG LIVESTOCK DISTRIBUTION

562
00:48:39,021 --> 00:48:41,148
[♪ dramatic music playing]

563
00:49:05,256 --> 00:49:06,382
[Hyeonsu] Captain!

564
00:49:27,111 --> 00:49:28,779
NEUROSURGEON KANG TAEJU

565
00:49:28,862 --> 00:49:29,905
SEYUN

566
00:49:44,878 --> 00:49:46,297
[music ends]

567
00:50:00,519 --> 00:50:02,521
[♪ tense music playing]

568
00:51:24,645 --> 00:51:26,814
STAIRWELL
FIRE DOOR, KEEP CLOSED

569
00:51:26,897 --> 00:51:29,900
DO NOT PLACE OBJECTS
NEAR FIRE DOOR

