00:51:50,087 --> 00:51:52,965
HEALTH CARE CENTER

571
00:51:53,048 --> 00:51:56,301
[beeping]
STYLE
::cue()

572
00:52:29,835 --> 00:52:30,836
[music ends]

573
00:52:46,143 --> 00:52:47,478
[grunts]

574
00:52:47,561 --> 00:52:49,813
-[vehicle approaching]
-[gasps]

575
00:52:53,817 --> 00:52:54,818
[sighs]

576
00:53:08,332 --> 00:53:09,833
WOORI TOGETHER MEDICAL CENTER

577
00:53:17,090 --> 00:53:18,342
[typing]

578
00:53:18,425 --> 00:53:22,262
LOGIN
ID: KTJ0630

579
00:53:25,849 --> 00:53:27,851
[ominous music plays]

580
00:53:44,618 --> 00:53:46,370
[grunts, pants]

581
00:53:55,337 --> 00:53:56,338
Ms. Ko!

582
00:53:57,965 --> 00:53:59,216
Ms. Ko!

583
00:54:04,680 --> 00:54:07,516
Ms. Ko, it's all over!

584
00:54:13,272 --> 00:54:14,273
[music ends]

585
00:54:18,610 --> 00:54:20,946
[♪ tense music plays]

586
00:54:21,613 --> 00:54:22,614
What are you doing?

587
00:54:24,783 --> 00:54:27,452
[grunting]

588
00:54:28,704 --> 00:54:30,038
Damn it!

589
00:54:31,290 --> 00:54:32,958
[grunts]

590
00:54:37,337 --> 00:54:40,173
[groans] What the hell is wrong with you?

591
00:54:41,466 --> 00:54:42,968
[screams]

592
00:54:44,886 --> 00:54:45,887
[grunts]

593
00:54:53,812 --> 00:54:54,813
Goddamnit!

594
00:55:15,751 --> 00:55:17,044
Last month…

595
00:55:17,127 --> 00:55:19,546
PATIENT FILES
DATE: JANUARY 2026

596
00:55:19,630 --> 00:55:20,631
APPLY

597
00:55:26,470 --> 00:55:29,473
[♪ pensive music playing]

598
00:55:33,685 --> 00:55:37,272
Okay, so what seems to be the problem?

599
00:55:37,356 --> 00:55:39,524
[Mr. Noh] My legs have been a little numb.

600
00:55:39,608 --> 00:55:43,320
My thighs feel tight, and they tingle
like they're being shocked.

601
00:55:43,403 --> 00:55:44,488
[mouse clicks]

602
00:55:46,615 --> 00:55:48,700
-[mouse clicks]
-"Male."

603
00:55:48,784 --> 00:55:50,535
SEX: MALE

604
00:55:50,619 --> 00:55:51,620
APPLY

605
00:55:53,955 --> 00:55:57,417
So, these symptoms mainly happen
when you're walking, right?

606
00:55:58,418 --> 00:56:01,797
Yeah. Well, not exactly all the time, but…

607
00:56:01,880 --> 00:56:04,257
-[mouse clicks]
-"In his forties."

608
00:56:05,592 --> 00:56:07,928
AGE: 40S

609
00:56:08,011 --> 00:56:10,389
APPLY
STYLE
::cue()

610
00:56:21,650 --> 00:56:26,697
[Taeju, whispers] "Ma Seongyeon,
nerve root compression."

611
00:56:26,780 --> 00:56:28,949
"Kim Duchan,

612
00:56:30,492 --> 00:56:33,161
dorsum foot pain."

613
00:56:33,245 --> 00:56:34,830
"Heo Jaeil…"

614
00:56:36,248 --> 00:56:39,084
"Feels like legs are being shocked…"

615
00:56:39,960 --> 00:56:42,879
"Radiating pain in both legs."

616
00:56:46,007 --> 00:56:49,219
"Intermittent neurogenic claudication."

617
00:56:51,304 --> 00:56:52,472
TINGLING SENSATION IN LEGS

618
00:56:52,556 --> 00:56:54,516
INTERMITTENT NEUROGENIC CLAUDICATION

619
00:56:55,267 --> 00:56:57,519
I'll write you a prescription
for about two weeks,

620
00:56:57,602 --> 00:56:59,187
and let's see how you feel by then.

621
00:57:01,898 --> 00:57:03,066
Okay, thank you.

622
00:57:13,410 --> 00:57:14,411
[music ends]

623
00:57:41,146 --> 00:57:43,815
BUTTON

624
00:57:43,899 --> 00:57:46,902
[♪ suspenseful music playing]

625
00:57:50,113 --> 00:57:54,910
BUTTON

626
00:57:58,705 --> 00:57:59,706
[gasps]

627
00:58:02,667 --> 00:58:04,419
[Seyun] What the hell? [breathes shakily]

628
00:58:09,674 --> 00:58:10,675
[Mr. Noh] Ms. Ko!

629
00:58:20,101 --> 00:58:21,269
"Heo Jaeil."

630
00:58:23,480 --> 00:58:25,148
"47-3, Yongho 3-gil."

631
00:58:25,232 --> 00:58:27,484
47-3, YONGHO 3-GIL,
ILWON-MYEON, YEOCHEON-SI

632
00:58:38,203 --> 00:58:39,412
Found you.

633
00:58:42,791 --> 00:58:47,629
THE HUSBAND

634
00:58:47,712 --> 00:58:50,006
[♪ closing theme playing]

635
00:59:28,712 --> 00:59:30,005
-Where are you going?
-[panting]

636
00:59:30,088 --> 00:59:31,840
Ms. Ko!

637
00:59:32,382 --> 00:59:34,217
[Taeju] I'm looking for her right now.

638
00:59:34,301 --> 00:59:35,844
I'm going to bring Seyun home.

639
00:59:35,927 --> 00:59:38,263
[Mr. Noh] Ms. Ko, I'm not mad yet. Okay?

640
00:59:38,346 --> 00:59:41,057
But if you keep this up,
I'm going to get really mad!

641
00:59:42,225 --> 00:59:43,894
Seyun…

642
00:59:43,977 --> 00:59:45,937
Help me! Please!

643
00:59:46,855 --> 00:59:48,064
Please help me.

644
00:59:48,148 --> 00:59:49,149
What's going on?

645
00:59:49,232 --> 00:59:52,319
It really is a scary world out there.

646
00:59:52,402 --> 00:59:54,571
How could someone do such a thing?

647
00:59:54,654 --> 00:59:55,530
[Mr. Noh] Mr. Kang?

648
00:59:55,614 --> 00:59:57,616
[Taeju] Manhui, I finally got your name.

649
00:59:57,699 --> 00:59:59,618
Talk. Where is my wife?

650
